        "de158e68-5d0d-4819-a625-e2dabdff87d1": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How it works",
            "heading_size": "medium",
            "icon": "help",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "collapse_icon": "carret",
            "display_top_border": true,
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>When you strike a tuning fork, it vibrates at a precise frequency measured in Hz (cycles per second). These frequencies interact with your body's natural rhythms:</p><p><strong>The Science:</strong> Each fork creates specific sound waves that trigger physiological responses. The 128Hz fork stimulates nitric oxide release in your cells within 30 seconds - the same molecule that won the 1998 Nobel Prize in Medicine for its healing properties.</p><p><strong>The Result:</strong> Your nervous system shifts from \"fight or flight\" to \"rest and digest.\" Blood pressure drops. Muscles relax. Mind clears. Sleep improves.</p><p><strong>It's that simple:</strong> No apps, no charging, no complicated techniques. Just pure physics working with your body's natural healing systems.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "margin_top": 24,
            "margin_bottom": 0
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_RDaXPM": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Instructions",
            "heading_size": "medium",
            "icon": "star",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "collapse_icon": "carret",
            "display_top_border": true,
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p><strong>Getting Started (2 minutes):</strong></p><ol><li>Find a quiet space and sit comfortably</li><li>Hold the tuning fork by the stem (never touch the prongs)</li><li>Strike the fork firmly with the activator - it should ring clearly</li><li>For weighted forks: Apply stem to body. For unweighted: Hold near ears</li></ol><p><strong>Your 4 Tuning Forks & How to Use Them:</strong></p><p><strong>128Hz & 136.1Hz Weighted Forks (with weights on ends):</strong></p><ul><li><strong>128Hz (C)</strong>: Your pain relief fork - press stem on sore joints, tight muscles, or spine</li><li><strong>136.1Hz (Om)</strong>: Your grounding fork - use on chest/heart area for deep calm</li><li>Both stimulate blood flow and release muscle tension</li><li>Limit to 2 applications per spot (more reduces effectiveness)</li></ul><p><strong>256Hz & 384Hz Unweighted Forks (no weights):</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Use separately</strong>: 256Hz for mental clarity, 384Hz for emotional balance</li><li><strong>Use together</strong>: Creates the \"perfect fifth\" - hold one near each ear</li><li>This harmony brings deep relaxation within 30 seconds</li><li>Balances left/right brain and harmonizes your entire energy field</li></ul><p><strong>Daily Routines:</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Morning (5 min)</strong>: Start with 136.1Hz on chest, then 256Hz near ears</li><li><strong>Afternoon (30 sec)</strong>: Quick 128Hz on temples for headache relief</li><li><strong>Evening (10 min)</strong>: Full sequence ending with 256Hz + 384Hz harmony</li><li><strong>As needed</strong>: 128Hz on any pain point for instant relief</li></ul><p><strong>Pro tip</strong>: The weighted forks work through vibration on the body. The unweighted forks work through sound near the ears. Both methods activate your body's natural healing response.</p><p><em>Full instructions included in your FREE Valmeris Guide</em></p>",
            "page": "",
            "margin_top": 24,
            "margin_bottom": 0
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_TdYymG": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Shipping",
            "heading_size": "medium",
            "icon": "local_shipping",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "collapse_icon": "carret",
            "display_top_border": true,
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>We offer free shipping for all orders over $45. Order processing<br/>takes 1-3 business days before shipment. Once your item/s is dispatched,<br/>the estimated delivery time is:</p><p>- USA: 8-12 business days<br/></p><p><strong>What's in Your Package:</strong></p><ul><li>4 precision tuning forks in protective sleeves</li><li>Premium activator</li><li>Professional carrying case</li><li>Quick start guide</li></ul>",
            "page": "",
            "margin_top": 24,
