            "collapse_icon": "carret",
            "display_top_border": true,
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p><strong>60-Day \"Love It or Return It\" Guarantee</strong></p><p><strong>Why we can offer this:</strong> 94% of customers keep their sets. The 6% who return typically say \"didn't use it enough\" - which is honest feedback we appreciate.</p><p><strong>Lifetime Warranty:</strong> Your tuning forks are guaranteed forever against defects. If one ever fails to ring true, we'll replace it free.</p>",
            "page": "",
            "margin_top": 24,
            "margin_bottom": 0
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_MrY8Ha": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
